data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 sided brick ranch-style home with a basement ! INSANT EQUITY - LISTED UNDER APPRAISED VALUE! This home is super charming, spacious, yet cozy! Beautiful curb appeal! Cul de sac location too! Gorgeous interior! You will love the kitchen featuring quartz counters, a stylish backsplash, stainless appliances, and a breakfast bar. The great room/dining room combo is open to the kitchen, making entertaining a breeze! A separate living room, too, would make an excellent place for you to work from home! Renovated tiled bathrooms! Full BASEMENT is unfinished and is waiting for your personal touch! You will love relaxing on your rear deck with stairs down to your huge and private tree-lined backyard - this gem is situated on over a third of an acre! It is a perfectly peaceful space to relax and kick back with family and friends! Come and see! Find out RIGHT NOW how you may qualify for UP TO 2% below-market interest rates.
